
* Ever wanted to send your friend some bitcoins as share of last nights taxi fee but don't know his wallet?
* Or wanted your friends to start using bitcoins but they won't install the client?
* Or want to use bitcoins easily from any mobile device?

**Use [Bitcoin-App.com](https://bitcoin-app.com)**

